Quickstrike:





Quickstrike walked to the Predacon's cave, meanwhile he hear the 
transmission from Bobertron. All he could do in reply to it was let out a 
healthy laugh. He gave no reply to it, just kept his path to the cave. 3rd 
in command? He was second in command.

He slowled his pace and looked behind himself to see if Lightmare was still 
following. He turned his head back around and kept moving. The 
scorpion/cobra made it back to base soon enough, just before the nightfall. 
He entered and transformed to robot mode. He stretched his arms out over his 
head and tilted his trunk back slightly.

Noticing Dark Mouse, he said, "Nice night ain't it?"
